        },
        {
          "context": "配置中文local环境第一步：编辑/var/lib/locales/supported.d/local，写入如zh_CN.UTF-8 UTF-8等内容。",
          "qas": [
            {
              "question": "配置中文local环境的第一步是什么？",
              "id": "5-463-7",
              "answers": [
                {
                  "text": "编辑/var/lib/locales/supported.d/local，写入如zh_CN.UTF-8 UTF-8等内容",
                  "answer_start": 19
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "context": "配置中文local环境第二步：生成相关locales，终端执行sudo locale-gen --purge。",
          "qas": [
            {
              "question": "配置中文local环境的第二步是什么？",
              "id": "5-463-8",
              "answers": [
